# Step 1: Create a hard link to file1\nln file1 temp_file1\n\n# Step 2: Use rsync to append file2 to file1\nrsync --append-verify file2 temp_file1\n\n# Step 3: Verify the concatenation\n# Optionally, you can compare the sizes or checksums of the original files to ensure correctness\n\n# Step 4: Remove the original files\nrm file1 file2\n\n# Step 5: Rename the concatenated file to the original file name\nmv temp_file1 file1